column171: Once shampoo has been rinsed off from the hair, gently squeeze the hair to reduce the remaining water.
column180: Use a wash cloth or hand towel to gently soak excess water.
column189: Allow the wig to air dry.
column198: When the wig is completely dry, shake the wig gently and brush into desired styles.
